                    <span>Secrets of Body Language is easy to read and understand. It's a very intuitive book on body language subtleties that you may have not noticed. Dozens of illustrations, good advance on conversation. Great for the well mannered who want to improve of their social graces in their professional lives. Also a great list of resources is included. 
